      <p class="center"><docType><b>EXPLANATORY MEMORANDUM TO</b></docType></p>
      <p class="center"><b>THE VALUE ADDED TAX (FLAT-RATE VALUATION OF SUPPLIES OF FUEL FOR PRIVATE USE) ORDER 2013</b></p>
      <p class="center"><docNumber><b>2013 No. 2911</b></docNumber></p>
    </preface>
